overview: Our Latest Release featuring the Epic South Australian 24 where the Motorbikin Team pull off a Podium Finish in the Big Bore Class and get 3 out of 4 bikes across the finish line!  Back it up with an Epic ride back to Queensland!  Following a high altitude GPS Route accross the New Zealand Alps  NZs Ultimate 2 up Destinations  A blast across the NSW Tablelands on a Pair of VSM Africa Twins
title: Motorbikin' 22: Thunder at Eudunda
